Module hu.unipannon.virt.plot
Package hu.unipannon.virt.plot.fluent

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.fluent.Plot
      • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.fluent.Log
  • public class Log
extends Plot
    Fluent interface responsible for creating a log scale line plot. This class initialises the controllers for the plot graphics, and applies the style elements from the FrameStyle and Line classes.
    Author:
    Tóth Bálint
